1.content:
kim possible had just her last lesson in middlton university and thought today she was free to do something with her friend monique.
as she began to store her books in her locker the pc in it came to life and wade contacted her.
"kim we have a problem" he said.
"what's the sitch wade" kim answered thinking there goes her free day.
"the military contacted me about a spike of quantum energy in a warehouse near the outskirts of middleton and asked us to investigate it"
"do we know who has something to do with it, wade" kim asked.
"i'm sorry, but no it seems the warehouse was used by different villains in the last year so it's hard to tell who is using it now"
"oh and kim be careful quantum energy is used for travel through time and space and you know what happened the last time you traveled through time" wade said.
"i know you don't need to remind me" kim sweat dropped. "i should go there now"

"wait don't you want to contact ron to meet up, kim"
"it's just a investigation wade and ron really needs his job"
1.title: a nearly normal day
